msgstr "معرف الإرسال:"

msgid "Your picture has been recorded!"
msgstr "تم تسجيل صورتك!"

msgid "Submission status:"
msgstr "حالة الإرسال:"

msgid "You have not submitted an image yet"
msgstr "لم ترسل صورة بعد"

